    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-4">Every relationship<br>is the mission.</h1>
    <p class="text-base text-white/60 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">We do not pursue capital. We pursue alignment. There is a meaningful difference.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-12 py-16">
    <button onclick="closeIR()" class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-primary hover:text-primary2 bg-transparent border-none cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-2 mb-12 p-0 transition-colors">&#x2190; Back to Pooled Impact Homepage</button>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-5 text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <p>We do not pursue capital. We pursue alignment. Capital that is misaligned with the mission — even at favorable terms — costs more than it contributes. We have chosen to grow slowly and build trust deliberately.</p>
        <p>Every investor conversation begins the same way: we listen first. We want to understand your values, your mandate, your constraints, and your vision before we describe ours.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-ink">Conduit Impact Capital</strong> is structured for institutional allocators who are moving beyond ESG labeling toward verifiable, machine-validated impact.</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-slate/40 pt-5 border-t border-rule leading-loose">Detailed fund materials available to qualified investors upon request. This page does not constitute an offer to sell or solicitation to buy securities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-rule rounded-sm p-8">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-6">Start a Conversation</h3>
        <div id="ir-form" class="space-y-4">
          <div><label class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-primary block mb-1.5">Full Name *</label>
          <input type="text" id="ir-name" placeholder="Your name" @input="trackAction('FORM.STARTCONVERSATION',{field:'name'})" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 border border-rule rounded-sm bg-paper text-sm outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors"></div>
          <div><label class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-primary block mb-1.5">Email *</label>
          <input type="email" id="ir-email" placeholder="you@organization.com" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 border border-rule rounded-sm bg-paper text-sm outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors"></div>
          <div><label class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-primary block mb-1.5">Phone <span class="font-sans normal-case tracking-normal text-slate/60">(optional)</span></label>
          <input type="tel" id="ir-phone" placeholder="(000) 000-0000" x-mask="(999) 999-9999" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 border border-rule rounded-sm bg-paper text-sm outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors"></div>
          <div><label class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-primary block mb-1.5">Organization</label>
          <input type="text" id="ir-org" placeholder="Institution or firm" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 border border-rule rounded-sm bg-paper text-sm outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors"></div>
