ass="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-white">Finance</h3><p class="text-xs text-white/60 mt-1">Conduit Impact Capital · Structured credit deployment</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-[3px]"><div class="cifer-card relative overflow-hidden flex-1"><div class="cifer-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621451537084-482c73073a0f?q=80&w=1674&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div><div class="cifer-overlay"><p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-secondary mb-1">C · Commodities</p><h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-white">Commodities</h3></div></div><div class="cifer-card relative overflow-hidden flex-1"><div class="cifer-img" style="background-image:url('https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1661782786426-8838b11a46bb?q=80&w=2069&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div><div class="cifer-overlay"><p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-secondary mb-1">R · Real Estate</p><h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-white">Real Estate</h3></div></div></div></div>
