<!-- PRINCIPLES -->
<section class="py-20 px-12 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
    <div>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-primary mb-4">How We Operate</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem)">Technology in service of truth.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <p>Pooled Impact is building Mountain Shift OS — an AI-powered operating system for impact-oriented organizations. Not AI as automation. <strong class="text-ink">AI as accountability.</strong></p>
        <p>Every capital deployment decision is checked against declared principles. The geometry of human flourishing is a design specification, not a metaphor.</p>
        <p>When a financial structure violates dignity, the system flags it. Declared truth, made operational.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="divide-y divide-rule"><div class="flex gap-5 py-5 border-b border-rule last:border-b-0"><div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-primary w-8 shrink-0 pt-0.5">L1</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Dignity</h4><p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Every person is made in the image of God. Every system we build reflects that — or it does not get built.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-5 py-5 border-b border-rule last:border-b-0"><div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-primary w-8 shrink-0 pt-0.5">L2</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Vulnerability</h4><p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">The people most affected by broken systems are the first consideration, not the last.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-5 py-5 border-b border-rule last:border-b-0"><div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-primary w-8 shrink-0 pt-0.5">L3</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Generation</h4><p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">We build for the people who cannot be in the room yet. The intergenerational thread is never cut.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-5 py-5 border-b border-rule last:border-b-0"><div class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-primary w-8 shrink-0 pt-0.5">L4</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Integrity of Exchange</h4><p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Every agreement, every transaction reflects what was promised. No gap between the word and the deed.</p></div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

